class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6} -->\n<h6>DENPASAR</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Regents School</li><li>Bali LightHouse</li><li>Green School Bali</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n[foogallery id=\"17\"]\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'School Partnership', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-06-02 17:48:55', '2020-06-02 17:48:55', '', 13, 'http://localhost:8080/kodekiddo2/13-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(31, 1, '2020-06-02 18:05:46', '2020-06-02 18:05:46', '<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"className\":\"pages\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull pages\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"center\",\"customTextColor\":\"#64bc46\",\"className\":\"the-minion p-heading header-title\"} -->\n<p style=\"color:#64bc46\" class=\"has-text-color has-text-align-center the-minion p-heading header-title\">OUR PROGRAM</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"align\":\"full\",\"className\":\"pages-body\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull pages-body\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"customTextColor\":\"#7650a1\",\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"has-text-color p-body alignfull\" style=\"color:#7650a1\"><strong>OUR APPROACH :</strong></h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignfull\">Kelas mencakup berbagai variasi cara belajar :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignfull\"><li>Group lesson: advisor menjelaskan konsep&nbsp;programming dengan menggunakan berbagai aktivitas di kelas tanpa komputer (‘unplugged’).</li><li>Personalized learning: anak menggunakan online platform untuk mengikuti pelajaran melalui&nbsp;video, coding exercise, solving puzzle, membuat&nbsp;video games. Aktivitas dilakukan secara individual sesuai&nbsp;dengan&nbsp;perkembangan masing-masing.</li><li>Group challenge: dalam group, team akan berkolaborasi mencari ide dan menggunakan&nbsp;coding untuk menggerakkan robot dan memecahkan masalah.</li><li>Kurikulum mencakup konsep computer science, computational thinking, dan matematika.</li><li>Jika murid tidak bisa datang ke center KodeKiddo, ada kelas online yang dapat dilakukan secara private/semi-private dengan instruktur KodeKiddo.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://kodekiddo.com/kelas-online-kodekiddo/\">Klik di sini untuk info kelas online.</a>&nbsp;</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":34,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"className\":\"img-left\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large img-left\"><img src=\"http://localhost:8080/kodekiddo2/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/block_code.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-34\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"customTextColor\":\"#7650a1\",\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"has-text-color p-body alignfull\" style=\"color:#7650a1\"><strong>OUR COURSES:</strong></h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"customTextColor\":\"#64bc46\",\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"has-text-color p-body alignfull\" style=\"color:#64bc46\">INTRODUCTION TO CODING</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignfull\"><li>Kelas berlangsung selama satu bulan (sekali seminggu, 90&nbsp;menit) untuk anak SD yang belum memiliki pengalaman programming.</li><li>Memperkenalkan konsep dasar programming&nbsp;</li><li>Menggunakan visual programming languages dan online platforms.</li><li>Mengerjakan simple software-hardware projects dengan robot Sphero, BB8, Dash.</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"customTextColor\":\"#64bc46\",\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"has-text-color p-body alignfull\" style=\"color:#64bc46\">CODING FOR&nbsp;SD BEGINNER (KELAS 1-4)</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignfull\">Kelas bertemu sekali&nbsp;/ dua kali seminggu selama 90&nbsp;menit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignfull\">Perkenalan konsep coding, Computational Thinking, dan computer science :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignfull\"><li>Menggunakan online platforms popular : Tynker, Kodu, CodeMonkey, Blockly, Scratch, Kodable</li><li>Memecahkan&nbsp;online puzzle dengan&nbsp;programming</li><li>Membuat animasi dan video game</li><li>Membuat custom&nbsp;Minecraft modding</li><li>Latihan computational thinking untuk kompetisi Bebras</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignfull\">Programming dengan robots :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignfull\"><li>Memprogram Sphero, BB-8, Dash robots</li><li>Mengontrol&nbsp;robot with block programming</li><li>Bekerja sama dalam group memecahkan masalah dengan programming</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"customTextColor\":\"#64bc46\",\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"has-text-color p-body alignfull\" style=\"color:#64bc46\">Coding for&nbsp;SD Advance (kelas 4-6)</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignfull\">Kelas bertemu sekali&nbsp;/ dua kali seminggu selama 90&nbsp;menit.Memperdalam konsep coding, Computational Thinking, dan computer science :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignfull\"><li>Menggunakan online platforms popular : Tynker, Scratch, CodeMonkey, MIT App Inventor, Grok Learning&nbsp;</li><li>Membuat animasi, video game, web pages, mobile apps</li><li>Membuat custom&nbsp;Minecraft mod</li><li>Latihan computational thinking untuk kompetisi Bebras</li><li>Perkenalan ke dasar text-based coding languages (HTML, Python, Java, C++, C, Javascript) dan konsep Artificial Intelligent – Maching Learning.&nbsp;</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignfull\">Programming dengan hardware :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignfull\"><li>Memprogram Sphero, BB-8, Dash, Cozmo robots dan circuit hardware Microbit, Makey-Makey</li><li>Mengontrol&nbsp;robot with block programming</li><li>Bekerja sama dalam group memecahkan masalah dengan programming</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"customTextColor\":\"#64bc46\",\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"has-text-color p-body alignfull\" style=\"color:#64bc46\">Coding for SMP</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignfull\">Kelas bertemu sekali&nbsp;/ dua kali seminggu selama 90&nbsp;menit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignfull\">Memperdalam konsep coding, Computational Thinking, dan computer science untuk level SMP :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignfull\"><li>Perkenalan dasar coding dengan menggunakan block programming dan dilanjutkan ke text-based coding languages (HTML, Python, Java, C++, C, Javascript)</li><li>Membuat animasi, websites, mobile apps, games dengan menggunakan programming</li><li>Latihan computational thinking untuk kompetisi Bebras</li><li>Perkenalan konsep Artificial Intelligent – Maching Learning</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignfull\">Programming dengan hardware :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignfull\"><li>Memprogram robot MakeBot, UB Kit, Dash</li><li>Implementasi coding ke circuit hardware Microbit, Makey-Makey, Arduino</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"customTextColor\":\"#64bc46\",\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"has-text-color p-body alignfull\" style=\"color:#64bc46\">CODING FOR SMA</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignfull\">Perkenalan ke programming dan dilanjutkan dengan eksplorasi coding di area berikut :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignfull\"><li>Game Development</li><li>Web Development</li><li>App Development</li><li>Computer Science, Algorithm, and Math in Coding&nbsp;</li><li>Data, Database and AI Intro for SMA&nbsp;</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignfull\">Setelah menyelesaikan kelas perkenalan tersebut, murid dapat memilih spesialisasi di bidang yang lebih spesifik :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignfull\"><li>Android App Development</li><li>Data Science</li><li>AI &amp; Machine Learning</li><li>Android App Development</li><li>iOS App Development</li><li>Python Programming</li><li>Algebra, Algorithm &amp; Programming</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignfull\"><strong>Persyaratan:</strong>&nbsp;Di dalam kelas anak akan menggunakan berbagai teknologi dan mengikuti online program berbahasa Inggris (instruksi di kelas diberikan dalam bahasa Indonesia). Supaya dapat mengikuti kelas, anak harus bisa&nbsp;menggunakan computer keyboard dan mouse dan mengerti&nbsp;bahasa Inggris dasar.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"customTextColor\":\"#7650a1\",\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"has-text-color p-body alignfull\" style=\"color:#7650a1\"><strong>OUR SCHEDULES :</strong></h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignfull\">Kelas berlangsung di hari biasa dan hari Sabtu :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignfull\"} -->\n<ul cla