li><li>Bekerja sama dalam group memecahkan masalah dengan programming</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"customTextColor\":\"#64bc46\",\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"has-text-color p-body alignwide\" style=\"color:#64bc46\">Coding for SMP</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignwide\">Kelas bertemu sekali&nbsp;/ dua kali seminggu selama 90&nbsp;menit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignwide\">Memperdalam konsep coding, Computational Thinking, dan computer science untuk level SMP :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignwide\"><li>Perkenalan dasar coding dengan menggunakan block programming dan dilanjutkan ke text-based coding languages (HTML, Python, Java, C++, C, Javascript)</li><li>Membuat animasi, websites, mobile apps, games dengan menggunakan programming</li><li>Latihan computational thinking untuk kompetisi Bebras</li><li>Perkenalan konsep Artificial Intelligent – Maching Learning</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignwide\">Programming dengan hardware :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignwide\"><li>Memprogram robot MakeBot, UB Kit, Dash</li><li>Implementasi coding ke circuit hardware Microbit, Makey-Makey, Arduino</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"customTextColor\":\"#64bc46\",\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"has-text-color p-body alignwide\" style=\"color:#64bc46\">CODING FOR SMA</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignwide\">Perkenalan ke programming dan dilanjutkan dengan eksplorasi coding di area berikut :&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignwide\"><li>Game Development</li><li>Web Development</li><li>App Development</li><li>Computer Science, Algorithm, and Math in Coding&nbsp;</li><li>Data, Database and AI Intro for SMA&nbsp;</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignwide\">Setelah menyelesaikan kelas perkenalan tersebut, murid dapat memilih spesialisasi di bidang yang lebih spesifik :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignwide\"><li>Android App Development</li><li>Data Science</li><li>AI &amp; Machine Learning</li><li>Android App Development</li><li>iOS App Development</li><li>Python Programming</li><li>Algebra, Algorithm &amp; Programming</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignwide\"><strong>Persyaratan:</strong>&nbsp;Di dalam kelas anak akan menggunakan berbagai teknologi dan mengikuti online program berbahasa Inggris (instruksi di kelas diberikan dalam bahasa Indonesia). Supaya dapat mengikuti kelas, anak harus bisa&nbsp;menggunakan computer keyboard dan mouse dan mengerti&nbsp;bahasa Inggris dasar.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"customTextColor\":\"#7650a1\",\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"has-text-color p-body alignwide\" style=\"color:#7650a1\"><strong>OUR SCHEDULES :</strong></h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignwide\">Kelas berlangsung di hari biasa dan hari Sabtu :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignwide\"><li>Senin, Selasa, Rabu, Kamis, atau Jumat 3:00-6:15 PM</li><li>Sabtu 8:30 – 6:00 PM</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"customTextColor\":\"#7650a1\",\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"has-text-color p-body alignwide\" style=\"color:#7650a1\"><strong>COURSE INVESTMENT :</strong></h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignwide\">Biaya registrasi Rp 200000 – 150000</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignwide\"><li>Kelas Introduction to Coding : Rp 350000 – 450000 / bulan</li><li>Kelas Coding for SD : Rp 500000 – 870000 / bulan</li><li>Kelas Coding for SMP : Rp 575000 – 1000000 / bulan</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignwide\">Hubungi masing-masing KodeKiddo center untuk mendapatkan detail harga dan discount :</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignwide\"><li>Referral discount</li><li>Sibling discount</li><li>Multi-month payment discount</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<p class=\"p-body alignwide\">KodeKiddo juga menyediakan beasiswa bagi murid yang membutuhkan.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->', 'Our Program', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '31-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-06-06 18:23:20', '2020-06-06 18:23:20', '', 31, 'http://localhost:8080/kodekiddo2/31-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
