c School, Tangerang Selatan</li><li>Karisma Bangsa, Tangerang Selatan</li><li>Sekolah Harapan Bangsa, Tangerang</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"p-body alignwide\">BANDUNG</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignwide\"><li>SD Penabur International School, Banda</li><li>SD Santo Yusup</li><li>Bandung Independent School</li><li>Mutiara Nusantara International School</li><li>SMP Bina Persada</li><li>SDK Trimulia HITS</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"p-body alignwide\">SEMARANG</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignwide\"><li>SIS Singapore Intercultural School – Semarang</li><li>Mondial School</li><li>Bina Bangsa School</li><li>Daniel Creative School</li><li>SD, SMP, SMA Kristen YSKI</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"p-body alignwide\">SURABAYA</h6>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<ul class=\"p-body alignwide\"><li>Sekolah Ciputra</li><li>IPH School – Surabaya Timur</li><li>Ivy School</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"align\":\"wide\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide\"><!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"className\":\"p-body alignwide\"} -->\n<h6 class=\"p-body alignwide\">YOGYAKA